title: Torben Storm
text:
Torben Storm (born 13 September 1946) is a Danish retired <a href="association%20football">football</a> player and <a href="Coach%20%28sport%29">coach</a> who played as a <a href="right%20midfielder">right midfielder</a>.
He played one game for the <a href="Denmark%20national%20under-19%20football%20team">Denmark under-19 national team</a> in 1964.
